# Design vocabulary

SSOT: `registries/design.registry.json` · validate with `codegenkit registry`.

## Hashtags (grill → `tags:`)

| Prefix | Example |
|--------|---------|
| `#shell:` | Registry-defined page/list shell |
| `#pattern:` | `CRUD` |
| `#ui:` | shadcn primitive |
| `#widget:` | form field |
| `#render:` | `text`, `chip` |
| `#style:` | `compact`, `flat` |
| `#needs-ui:` | planned widget — prototype implements |

Shell names and custom-template behavior are adapter/product registry data. Do
not assume a Nuxt `.vue` shell in a Next.js target or vice versa.

## Grill

1. BA bullet → `lookupAlias()` in registry
2. Low confidence → ask member
3. `codegenkit gen:dry --id …` must pass.

Do not invent component names outside the selected adapter registry.
